10
00:00:25,160 --> 00:00:28,490
The input it provides complements
stimuli coming from the real world,

11
00:00:28,490 --> 00:00:30,510
and instead of just replacing them.

12
00:00:30,510 --> 00:00:32,310
And that creates some
enormous challenges, but

13
00:00:32,310 --> 00:00:35,190
also some really incredible
opportunities as well.

14
00:00:35,190 --> 00:00:37,960
Imagine the devices that can integrate
directly into our everyday lives,

15
00:00:37,960 --> 00:00:39,620
enhancing our reality.

16
00:00:39,620 --> 00:00:42,770
Imagine systems that could, for example,
automatically translate text or

17
